com.unvired.sync.notifier
Interface NotificationListener

public interface NotificationListener

The listener interface for receiving notification events. The class that is interested in processing a notification event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the SyncEngine's addNotificationListener method. When the notification event occurs, that object's appropriate method is called back.
